00:00:00,500 --> 00:00:08,900
What? You call me out just to let me watch you drink tea?

2
00:00:08,900 --> 00:00:11,900
I just wanted to give you another chance to work for me.

3
00:00:11,900 --> 00:00:14,900
Why? Because you couldn't handle them by yourself.

4
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:16,899
And how far have you got with your planning?

5
00:00:16,899 --> 00:00:20,899
I bet you haven't even stepped foot inside their door, have you?

6
00:00:20,899 --> 00:00:23,899
What is in it for me if I work with you?

7
00:00:23,899 --> 00:00:27,899
No, direct benefits. But I can help mitigate some of the losses.

8
00:00:27,899 --> 00:00:33,560
I would have thought that a man like you on the surface...

9
00:00:33,560 --> 00:00:36,560
A wealthy young man from an upper-class family

10
00:00:36,560 --> 00:00:40,560
would be involved in such scandalous affairs.

11
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:43,750
Living together and taking lewd photographs.

12
00:00:43,750 --> 00:00:45,750
Mine, mine, mine.

13
00:00:45,750 --> 00:00:46,750
What do you want?

14
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:48,750
Well, that depends if you're willing to work for me.

15
00:00:48,750 --> 00:00:52,780
Otherwise, I'm not sure where these photographs will end up.

16
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:57,189
Go to hell.

17
00:00:57,189 --> 00:01:01,820
I've prepared a surprise for you.

18
00:01:01,820 --> 00:01:04,819
The next time you meet, you'll be begging me to help.

